metadata.name: Oracle of Liberty
metadata.description:
The 'Oracle of Liberty' is more than just a work of art - recognize its origin and you will realize that it hides more than it shows.  
The sound of the Oracle whispers in the minds of pioneers and creatives. But can you hear it?  
Those who have the courage to trust the oracle will be rewarded. Whoever possesses it also possesses the key to a new world of possibilities. So take it firmly in your hand and let the Oracle unfold its wonders in your life.
